## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the potential bias in sources. Some data points may vary due to differences in reporting standards and methodologies across organizations. Additionally, the report focuses primarily on financial aspects of aid, potentially overlooking other critical factors such as political and social impacts. Further research is needed to explore these dimensions comprehensively.